These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, musical, action, disaster, mystery
There are 6 different favourite colors: white, blue, ivory, purple, emerald, aquamarine
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
8. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire  | musical    | action  | time-travel      | disaster    |
| Color      | blue  | aquamarine | emerald | white | purple | ivory |

