.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: poppy, orchid, tulip, iris, sunflower, balloon-flower
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, hiking, filmmaking, puzzles, board-games, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
9. the person who growspoppy is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Flower   | poppy   | sunflower | orchid | balloon-flower | iris     | tulip  |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | hiking    | writing      | dancing  | puzzles | board-games |

