.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, aconite, amaryllis, bellflower, zinnia
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, surfing, swimming, weightlifting, parkour
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growsamaryllis##1
9. the person who growsaconite is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | zinnia   | bellflower      | begonia | marigold  | aconite   |
| Sport   | surfing | parkour | skiing | climbing   | weightlifting | swimming |

