.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, may, january, november, august, april
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, spinach, corn, pumpkin, peach, pomegranate
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
8. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Birthday   | january  | november | october      | may  | april | august |
| Food     | cauliflower | pomegranate  | peach | corn | pumpkin  | spinach    |

