.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
City: london, rome, hannover, colone, boston, liverpool
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, water, 7up, soy-milk, juice
 1. the person drinking water is the person traveling to london##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| City         | colone | liverpool | london | boston | rome | hannover  |
| Beverage   | juice  | 7up  | water  | milk | soy-milk      | almond-milk |

