3. the architect is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the librarian is the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the scientist is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Birthday   | september    | april    | february | october     | july   | june     |
| Job   | librarian | security-guard | freelancer | dressmaker | architect | scientist |

