3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating potato is the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta  | scrabble     | poker    | chess  | go          |
| Food         | potato  | onion | grapefruit | lemon | broccoli | asparagus |

